Interface SortedList<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of the elements stored in this collection.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<E>, Iterable<E>, List<E>, Sorted<E>

    public interface SortedList<E>
extends List<E>, Sorted<E>
    Acts like a list with elements in a specific order. Adds behavior to return a headList and tailList plus behavior taken from sorted.
    Author:
    Jacob Malter
